title: Bernoulli-Euler-Kommission
text: The Bernoulli-Euler-Kommission of the Bernoulli-Euler-Gesellschaft is the scientific society of the Swiss Academie of Science (SCNAT) which is dedicated to the promotion of the scientific contribution of members of the Bernoulli family members and Leonhard Euler.
